Motopanser G Variant was created/rendered by Thobie Buntaran a.k.a. Loreng on 06 October 2021, Mantrijeron, Yogyakarta, Indonesia.

A hybrid of a motorcycle & panzer with ultra biodynamic & mechanical design, with a top speed of 300000 km/s or 186000 mi/s.
Designed in the 3020s and manufactured in Santuari Lab by Loreng, this automobile species is specially made for interplanetary transportation & crystal harvesting.
Sculpted and modelled based on the biological anatomy of Valanga nigricornis, commonly known as the Javanese grasshopper.
This species can reproduce both in sexual and asexual (parthenogenesis) in times when reproductive opportunities are limited. 

Motopanser G Variant's first appearance was in “Operation Jade Fury” (AD 3021), during the initial launch of the Santuarian Colonialist in a nearby habitable planet led by Rocky.
